[In this posting, the breakdown of age range does show some cases of pertussis in individuals over 65 years old. These are either people who were not immunized as children or who are waning in immunity for the old whole-cell killed vaccine. It would be interesting to know whether any of the cases in infants were spread from those who had received the old vaccine. - Mod.LL

